  <compounddef id="getting_started_page" kind="page">
    <compoundname>getting_started_page</compoundname>
    <title>Getting Started with AnalysisG</title>
    <briefdescription>
<para>A step-by-step guide to using the AnalysisG framework. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<sect1 id="getting_started_page_1gs_overview">
<title>Overview</title>
<para>AnalysisG is a framework for graph-based analysis in high-energy physics. This guide walks you through the basic concepts and workflow.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="getting_started_page_1gs_concepts">
<title>Key Concepts</title>
<sect2 id="getting_started_page_1gs_events">
<title>Events</title>
<para>An <bold>event</bold> represents a single physics collision. In AnalysisG, you define how to read event data by subclassing <ref refid="classevent__template" kindref="compound">event_template</ref>.</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="getting_started_page_1gs_particles">
<title>Particles</title>
<para><bold>Particles</bold> are physics objects within an event (electrons, muons, jets, etc.). Define particle types by subclassing <ref refid="classparticle__template" kindref="compound">particle_template</ref>.</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="getting_started_page_1gs_graphs">
<title>Graphs</title>
<para><bold>Graphs</bold> transform events into graph structures suitable for machine learning. Particles become nodes, and relationships become edges. Define graphs by subclassing <ref refid="classgraph__template" kindref="compound">graph_template</ref>.</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="getting_started_page_1gs_selections">
<title>Selections</title>
<para><bold>Selections</bold> filter events based on physics criteria. Define selections by subclassing <ref refid="classselection__template" kindref="compound">selection_template</ref>.</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="getting_started_page_1gs_models">
<title>Models</title>
<para><bold>Models</bold> are neural networks that process graph data. Define models by subclassing <ref refid="classmodel__template" kindref="compound">model_template</ref>.</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="getting_started_page_1gs_metrics">
<title>Metrics</title>
<para><bold>Metrics</bold> evaluate model performance. Define metrics by subclassing <ref refid="classmetric__template" kindref="compound">metric_template</ref>.</para>
</sect2>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="getting_started_page_1gs_workflow">
<title>Typical Workflow</title>
<para><orderedlist>
<listitem><para><bold>Define your data structure</bold><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Create event template(s)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Create particle template(s)</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Define your graph representation</bold><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Create graph template(s)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Specify which particles become nodes</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Define edge topology</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Add features (data and truth)</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Define selections</bold> (optional)<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Create selection template(s)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Implement selection criteria</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Define your model</bold><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Create model template</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Implement forward pass</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Configure and run analysis</bold><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Create analysis instance</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Add samples, templates, models</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Configure settings</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Start execution</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="getting_started_page_1gs_example">
<title>Minimal Example</title>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="preprocessor">#include<sp/>&lt;<ref refid="analysis_8h" kindref="compound">AnalysisG/analysis.h</ref>&gt;</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#include<sp/>&lt;<ref refid="event__template_8h" kindref="compound">templates/event_template.h</ref>&gt;</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#include<sp/>&lt;<ref refid="graph__template_8h" kindref="compound">templates/graph_template.h</ref>&gt;</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Minimal<sp/>event<sp/>template</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">class<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">SimpleEvent<sp/>:<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">public</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="classevent__template" kindref="compound">event_template</ref><sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">public</highlight><highlight class="normal">:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>SimpleEvent()<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><ref refid="namespacename" kindref="compound">name</ref><sp/>=<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;simple_event&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Minimal<sp/>graph<sp/>template</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">class<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">SimpleGraph<sp/>:<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">public</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="classgraph__template" kindref="compound">graph_template</ref><sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">public</highlight><highlight class="normal">:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>SimpleGraph()<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><ref refid="namespacename" kindref="compound">name</ref><sp/>=<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;simple_graph&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">void</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="classgraph__template_1af6db04c1f266cc1d7da481e52784a30d" kindref="member">CompileEvent</ref>()</highlight><highlight class="keyword"><sp/>override<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Add<sp/>features<sp/>here</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>main()<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><ref refid="classanalysis" kindref="compound">analysis</ref><sp/>ana;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a7142e8c027e12fc8b46e0045f733e107" kindref="member">m_settings</ref>.output<sp/>=<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;output/&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1ad49ba744577bd6d17f83efa48909f767" kindref="member">add_samples</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;/data/&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;sample&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a6d71bcd8dfe9deb47acba686df1e0058" kindref="member">add_event_template</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">new</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>SimpleEvent(),<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;sample&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a03e15b76f9271d2c98f094cd7cdb3863" kindref="member">add_graph_template</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">new</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>SimpleGraph(),<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;sample&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a401745bb4bcae03160ffa0b5df2887e7" kindref="member">start</ref>();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordflow">return</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>0;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
